name: I DO NOT WANT TO BE A BREADED FISH !!
name_original: I DO NOT WANT TO BE A BREADED FISH !!
description:
3 levels of pure sea's salt. A good way to experience the breath of the sea. Your fish is at the edge of full panic, this is your job to save him from terrible breaded fish eaters.

Made by :

Jules Rouault (Polipot)

Rémi Glénission (Urhkas)
